Added driver to interface with mochad. No implementation yet. Added missing getDriver and getController methods to interfaces that needed it. This way we can traverse through the structure. Added toString() to a few classes.

Added UPS, IUPS, and an APC UPS driver partial implementation.
Added write function to our mochad driver implementation.
Added basic DB functionality and implemented the database model for Zone.
Done defining DeviceModel, ControllerModel and ZoneModel. Closes #1.
Added constructor methods to ControllerModel and DeviceModel.
